{"tid":1499344,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［航空業核彈］應該做，即刻做！","createTime":"2019-08-23T16:24:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T00:33:23.000Z","uid":23830,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0e13b73a7dd5e4500ca81fc5a235d4f1e4b04e07","tid":1499344,"uid":23830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:24:20.000Z","msg":"之前講過<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">航空業罷工</span></strong></span>係一個核彈。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>呢粒核彈一定要引爆！<br />\n</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n呢一爆可以取回氣勢，乘勢追擊，無論全機場罷工好抑或只CX或港龍員工或機組人員罷工好，尤其係<span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>機師表態罷工最有力，迫在停機坪費都俾到航空公司肉痛，他們必須合作，</strong></span></span>大家同一條船，不容許白色恐怖和限制人身和言論自由。<br />\n<br />\n這是見血封喉的一招，唔係人人懂揸飛機和服務航班。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">CX同港龍嘅機師，出手啦！</span></span>"},{"pid":"e3562f291d37362434c4e986973c80f206ef9459","tid":1499344,"uid":23830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T00:01:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8f99ec55883e5693f32b65bc959585d6c9e329ff","tid":1499344,"uid":59824,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T00:14:28.000Z","msg":"其實依家政府就最撚驚航空，機場個啲罷工，停運<br />\n一停運就連鎖效應咁搞埋其他行業同國家<br />\n<br />\n所以一定要引爆呢個核彈<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">五大訴求！缺一不可！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">-------------分隔線------------<br />\n大家介唔介意抽少少時間幫我做份大學問卷，淨係想要100份🙏，連登咁多人，希望可以幫下手，我順便推下post，thanks🙏<br />\nBtw 連登有愛，多謝有二百幾人關心我份問卷，但要更多謝幫我填咗個廿幾位🙏 問卷有啲長，可能會用你少少時間，對唔住🙏<br />\n<a href=\"https://surveyhero.com/c/682e889d\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsurveyhero.com%2Fc%2F682e889d&d=iLyAB%2BOE6twWPMF9W2uC6jUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=a7a64f4e\" target=\"_blank\">https://surveyhero.com/c/682e889d</a></span>"},{"pid":"dbf84f28e28e4a78f0d48447b9344202867ce918","tid":1499344,"uid":126099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T00:23:16.000Z","msg":"Push!"},{"pid":"d40bd07c2daf9cbcc39e3c09da5c5461905d96aa","tid":1499344,"uid":276150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T00:33:23.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}